  N5 --> N6[UI: Data View / UI Screen / dashboard - Surface consolidated KPI and exception report for review (promo ROI, waste reduction, COGS impact)]
  N6 --> Z1[Outcome: Consistent SKU/location master and requirement datasets across systems, prioritized exceptions for human review, automated rebalances/PO adjustments where safe to act, reduced spoilage and stock imbalances, improved promotional ROI and lower COGS from timely material-data corrections.]
  N3 -->|Data quality checks fail (missing or ...| B1[Do not auto-update; create CWB Lifecycle exception and send Action Item to data steward with failing records]
